name: Glassbreakers: Champions of Moss
summary:
Squad Up.
Build your squad from a dynamic roster of 12 Champions each with unique abilities and roles that shape how you counter, combo, and control the match. With deep customization, your squad’s style will be unmistakably your own.

Face Off.
Battle friends in private matches, test your skill in ranked duels, or refine your strategy in AI skirmishes. Each fight is a tactical and tactile showdown. Adapt to your opponent’s squad and command your Champions...
